reviewText: This was UNGODLY bad.....on so many levels.......I practically don't know where to start with this critique. Julie Strain & Julie Smith are 2 of my personal favorite Penthouse models from the past. Somehow, I knew I was in for a treat. APRIL FOOLS on me! All this DVD succeeded in accomplishing was raise my anger level a couple of notches. God.......I HATE wasting money.
Do not waste your money on this 3D Retro Glamour Girls DVD.  Not worth it at all spend money on something worth watching.
